name: joinvoice
description: Have DJ Ino join a voice channel of your choosing. You can then have Ino play music for you.

name: playtrack
description: Have DJ Ino play a track in the voice channel he is in. This supports both individual Youtube URL and Youtube playlist urls.

options.name: track
options.description: The URL to the track you want to play

name: pause
description: DJ Ino will pause the current track, if one is playing

name: listqueue
description: DJ Ino will list all tracks currently in the queue.

name: skip
description: DJ Ino will skip the current track and play the next track in the queue.
